&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uncapped Commission&lt;/strong&gt;: Performance-driven with no ceiling on your earnings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On Target Earnings (OTE)&lt;/strong&gt;: $115,000 – $125,000&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: 100% Remote (U.S. Based)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working Hours:&lt;/strong&gt; 8:30 am – 5:30 pm (EST) -- We are prioritizing candidates that live in the Eastern time zone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel:&lt;/strong&gt; Minimal (approx. 5%) for team off-sites or strategic meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Top-Tier Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt; 100% company-paid medical premiums for employees and a generous 401(k) match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
